  <p><strong>... Ah yes, Christmas</strong> is upon us, and we're about to say farewell to another decade, and a very significant one for so many reasons and for so many people. Incedo's decade has been huge, we didn't exist a decade ago and for those of you who welcomed the new millennium in with YFC, could you have imagined where we'd be today? There&rsquo;s sure to be mixed feelings and great memories that you hold onto.</p>
  <p>As Christmas approaches and the New Year arrives, let&rsquo;s make it our desire to respectfully remember the past, and then move our gaze to the future, the telling of a new story, a clean slate of a new mission in a new decade. Incedo is on the move, we are evolving, shaping and forging new paths of mission and ways of bringing young people on our faith adventure. What will Incedo's story be at the end of the 2010's?</p>
